    "This simplified interaction reduces the learning curve, making the creation of narrative visualizations more accessible to a broader audience.",
    "The natural language processing capabilities of foundation models enable them to comprehend and generate a wide range of semantic information, allowing them to handle complex user commands and natural language queries.",
    "Foundation models can not only understand the user's intent but also generate precise responses and recommendations tailored to specific needs [7].Enhancing User Interaction through Exploratory Interaction.",
